<h2><U>HOW TO APPLY VISA</U> </h2>
<p><b> To apply visa You should follow the following steps. </b></p>
<button class="collapsible">Step 1</button>
<div class="content">
  <p>Select a visa subclass which is appropriate for the purpose of your travel to Sri Lanka and download the relevant visa application form.</p>
</div>

<button class="collapsible">Step 2</button>
<div class="content">
  <p>Your visa application may require supporting documentation. For a list of supporting documentation required for your visa</p>

<b><font size="4">What are the documents I need to submit with my Residence visa application ?</font></b></br>
<b><u>BOI</u></b>
<ul>
<li>BOI certificate</li>
<li>Request Letter from the representing Company</li>
<li>BOI Agreement</li>
<li>Company Registration certificate</li>
<li>Recomondation from the respective Ministry</li>
<li>A copy of the Bio Data Page of Your passport</li>
</ul>

<b><u>Project</u></b>
<ul>
<li>Project Office Request</li>
<li>Recommendation of Line Ministry OR Recommendation of Dept. of External Resources</li>
<li>Agreement of Project</li>
<li>A copy of the Bio Data Page of Your passport</li>
</ul>

</div>
<button class="collapsible">Step 3</button>
<div class="content">
  <p> Organise payment of the visa fees in the form of a bank draft from a Sri Lankan bank.</p>
</div>

<button class="collapsible">Step 4</button>
<div class="content">
  <p>Make an appointment with the AVAC during the stipulated submission times to lodge your application and submit your biometrics. Please carry a printout of your appointment confirmation and attend your appointment 15mins prior at AVAC. </p>
<p><b> <font size="4">What are document i should take to the appointment ?</font> </b>
<li> One copy of your passport</li>
<li> Should bring the appointment Receipt  </li>
</p>

</div>

<button class="collapsible">Step 5</button>
<div class="content">
  <p> Lodge your visa application and submit your biometrics at the AVAC. The Sri Lanka Visa Office may contact you to request additional information. </p> </br>

</div>
